extendedInfo.description: With access to over 6,300 locations nationwide, the CU Service Centers Shared Branching Network makes your credit union one of the most convenient financial institutions in the world and with the Locator app, it just got even more convenient.Call us at 888-372-2669 or visit www.fscc.com for more details.

reviews.title: Terrible
reviews.comment: Uses the old map interface, doesn\'t send street number for navigation, doesn\'t list info such as restricted access or cash free facility, leaves navigation on. Don\'t waste your space.
reviews.author: Charles Bosse

reviews.title: Good Start
reviews.comment: After all the bugs are out and all the locations are in, it will be great. I use Allshare and Shared banking alot and it realy helps.  Everything does not work perfect from the start, give it time.
reviews.author: Bernice Robinson

reviews.title: Gps stays on
reviews.comment: Need exit command or whatevr to turn off gps aftr query
reviews.author: rick brakeman

reviews.title: Replaced
reviews.comment: This formerly great app has been replaced (per the \"about\" button) with an app called Sprig. It\'s more functional.
reviews.author: Andy Knight

reviews.comment: Garbage... more like a 7-11 app because that\'s where it sends you. Neither of my 2 credit unions were listed. In fact, no credit unions were listed.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: App is a god send. Cu may have only 3 branches but finding co-ops with the app is a true life saver. Finally a useful app. Thank you thank you!!!!!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Almost perfect
reviews.comment: If this app included a search for the surcharge-free ATM locations in the co-op network, then this would be a 5-star review.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Simple enough
reviews.comment: It does what it says.  I travel all over the world and having access to my different CU accounts is a easy when you can find a branch nearby.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Very helpful. Give directions, bank hours. Will highly recommend this download!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Useless app
reviews.comment: I have yet to get this thing to actually work. Every time I try to search for branches, it force closes or freezes up my phone. Piece of crap, not worth installing. Don\'t even bother. I even tried several times to uninstall and then reinstall it. Same outcome.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Crashes all the time, address doesn\'t carry over to gps.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Sweet!!!
reviews.comment: Having a credit union based in TX limits where I can go, and with this app I always know which bank I can use any where I\'m at!!!!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Needs a way to filter the search
reviews.comment: There needs to be some way to search for just ATMs or just shared branches. It isn\'t very useful in its current state.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: SD card storage needed! Also, GPS stays on after closing app unless you exit by hitting the back button. Very useful app though.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Totally awesome! Never worry about cash again
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Basic
reviews.comment: Needs some fine tuning but serves its purpose. Screen size doesn\'t fit my ATRIX 2.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Locate free ATMs
reviews.comment: I love this app. Helps me find an ATM wherever I need one so I don\'t have to pay bank fees.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Helpful
reviews.comment: Works great. Accurate. Cuts out unnecessary travel time. Wish there was a way to search credit unions that also do transaction in branch.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Just wanted to let you know how great I think this app is! I drive a lot for my job I don\'t always know exactly where a cu is and this app helps!!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Has Potential
reviews.comment: The app has potential to be a lot better... however it currently is severly out of date, supporting only low res screens and displaying only branches, but not atms or other data.
reviews.author: A Google User
